short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bookmarker is a simple Chrome extension to search bookmarks.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The omnibox is limited to only six search results, including the web and bookmarts. However, there is no way to explicitly search bookmarks. Bookmarker solves this problem. Type "bb" in the omnibox and start searching!
